{"id":"kehua_spi_utility","fabricante":"Kehua","familia":"utility","modo":"matricial","pdf_chars":2298,"texto":"Three-phase On-grid String Inverter\nSPI50K~60K-B X2 Series\nGrid friendly\n• Grid-connected current harmonics\n<3%, green adapts to grid\n• Ultra wide grid voltage range\nSafe and reliable\n• IP66 and optional C5 anti-corrosion\ngrade, intelligent fan with IP68\nprotection\n• Integrated DC&AC SPD\nHigh Yield\n• 4/5 MPPTs design with max\nefficiency 98.8%\n• Up to 20A max current per PV\nstring, compatible with large current/\nbifacial modules\nEasy O&M\n• Optional intelligent I-V and fault wave\nrecording, quick failure analysis\n• Key components life optimization\ndesign Reduce failure risk\nTechnical Specification\nItems \tSPI50K-B X2 \tSPI60K-B X2\nDC Input (PV)\nMax. PV input voltage \t1100Vdc\nRated input voltage \t600Vdc\nMax.current per MPPT \t40A\nNo. of MPPTs \t4 \t5\nNo. of PV strings per MPPT \t2\nMPPT voltage range \t180~1000Vdc\nStarting voltage \t180Vdc\nDC switch \tYes\nAC Output (On-grid)\nRated AC output power \t50kW \t60kW\nMax. output power \t55kVA \t66kVA\nRated AC output voltage \t380/400Vac\nRated output current \t72.2A \t86.6A\nMax. output current \t79.4A \t95.3A\nRated grid frequency \t50Hz/60Hz\nGrid frequency range \t45~55Hz/55~65Hz\nPower factor \t>0.99 (rated power)\nAdjustable power factor \t0.8 (leading)~0.8 (lagging)\nTHDi \t<3% (rated power)\nEfficiency*\nMax. efficiency \t98.70% \t98.80%\nEuropean efficiency \t98.40% \t98.45%\nMPPT efficiency \t99.90%\nFunction and protection\nAnti-islanding \tYes\nDC(PV) reversed connection \tYes\nAC short circuit protection \tYes\nTemperature protection \tYes\nAFCI function \tYes (optional)\nIntegrated PID function \tYes (optional)\nIV curve scan and diagnosis \tYes (optional)\nZero-export function \tYes (optional)\nSurge protection \tDC Type II & AC Type II\nGeneral\nDimensions (W*H*D) \t670*490*284 mm\nWeight \t55kg\nIP grade \tIP66\nSelf-consumption at night \t<1W\nCooling type \tIntelligent forced air cooling\nAltitude \t4000m (>3000m derating)\nOperating temperature \t-35ºC~60ºC\nRelative humidity \t0~100%\nDisplay \tLED+APP\nDC terminal \tMC4 Terminal\nAC terminal \tOT Terminal\nInstallation method \tWall-mounted\nCommunication \tWIFI ,RS485,4G (optional)\nCompliance EN 62109-1/2, IEC 62109-1/2, EN IEC 61000-6-2/4, IEC 61727, IEC 62116,\nCEI 0-16, CEI 0-21, EN 50549-1,EN 50549-10, NC RfG\n● \t*Data under laboratory test conditions.\n● \tSpecifications are subject to change without prior notice.\n\n-- 1 of 1 --\n\n","tokens":[{"page":1,"x":57,"y":732,"s":"Three-phase On-grid String Inverter"},{"page":1,"x":57,"y":712,"s":"SPI50K~60K-B X2 Series"},{"page":1,"x":353,"y":527,"s":"Grid friendly"},{"page":1,"x":353,"y":506,"s":"•"},{"page":1,"x":359,"y":506,"s":"Grid-connected current harmonics"},{"page":1,"x":359,"y":494,"s":"<3%, green adapts to grid"},{"page":1,"x":353,"y":481,"s":"•"},{"page":1,"x":359,"y":481,"s":"Ultra wide grid voltage range"},{"page":1,"x":353,"y":653,"s":"Safe and reliable"},{"page":1,"x":353,"y":632,"s":"•"},{"page":1,"x":358,"y":632,"s":"IP66 and optional C5 anti-corrosion"},{"page":1,"x":359,"y":620,"s":"grade, intelligent fan with IP68"},{"page":1,"x":359,"y":609,"s":"protection"},{"page":1,"x":353,"y":596,"s":"•"},{"page":1,"x":358,"y":596,"s":"Integrated DC&AC SPD"},{"page":1,"x":111,"y":653,"s":"High Yield"},{"page":1,"x":111,"y":630,"s":"•"},{"page":1,"x":116,"y":630,"s":"4/5 MPPTs design with max"},{"page":1,"x":117,"y":619,"s":"efficiency 98.8%"},{"page":1,"x":111,"y":606,"s":"•"},{"page":1,"x":116,"y":606,"s":"Up to 20A max current per PV"},{"page":1,"x":117,"y":595,"s":"string, compatible with large current/"},{"page":1,"x":117,"y":584,"s":"bifacial modules"},{"page":1,"x":111,"y":527,"s":"Easy O&M"},{"page":1,"x":111,"y":506,"s":"•"},{"page":1,"x":116,"y":506,"s":"Optional intelligent I-V and fault wave"},{"page":1,"x":117,"y":495,"s":"recording, quick failure analysis"},{"page":1,"x":111,"y":483,"s":"•"},{"pa